ALBANY, Dec. 1 (AP)—The State Barge Canal System will close Monday morning for the winter, the State Transporta tion Department said today. The Erie Canal, from the Hud son River to Lake Erie; the Champlain Canal, from the Hudson River to Lake Cham plain, and the Oswego Canal, from the Erie Canal to Lake Ontario will be affected. The Cayuga‐Seneca Canal, con necting Cayuga and Seneca Lakes with the Erie Canal, closed yesterday.